We did have transport to/from the airport arranged in advance by water taxi and that was worth the extra money since it was just my daughter and myself traveling.	The location of the hotel was good, close to water transport, good shopping and lovely restaurants.	The hotel is affordable and in a great location - easy to walk to the train station as well as to all of the great sights and water taxi stops.	The location was good for us because it was right near the boat to go to the airport and was about a 15-20 minute walk from the train station, but we made it with our luggage.